    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a dependable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Most electronic features work, though the rear power windows are slow and the AC takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its age and mileage.",
