    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, making it the perfect pick if you want something dependable without paying those 'brand new' prices. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it's the right fit for you!",
