      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. The drivetrain utilizes a robust ZF 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To address common chassis fatigue, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein B16 dampers, providing superior rebound and compression characteristics over stock. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the mechanical tolerances and throttle response remain exceptionally tight. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
