      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver and it's been such a joy to own. This car is in great shape, runs super smooth, and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect companion for weekend getaways or just getting around town with ease. Come take it for a test drive\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 33500.0,
