    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound Porsche Cayman S featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). This mid-engine platform delivers exceptional torsional rigidity and near-perfect weight distribution, ensuring neutral handling through high-G corners. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, precise throws, while the ventilated cross-drilled rotors provide significant thermal resistance and stopping power. Though the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is robust, with no signs of bore scoring or oil seepage. Equipped with staggered alloy wheels and a tuned exhaust note, this 987.2 generation is a benchmark for analog driver engagement and mechanical reliability.",
